00:11:42.082 --> 00:11:43.295
Chikki, ini...
- Apa?

00:11:43.375 --> 00:11:45.145
Kami tidak memiliki kulkas.

00:11:46.495 --> 00:11:47.895
Kami tidak punya apa-apa.

00:11:49.382 --> 00:11:50.332
Chikki.

00:11:52.184 --> 00:11:53.046
Terus?

00:11:53.869 --> 00:11:55.819
Kami memiliki keberanian, keberanian,

00:11:56.216 --> 00:11:57.041
dan keluarga.

00:11:57.122 --> 00:11:59.155
Anda mengatakannya dua kali.

00:12:03.345 --> 00:12:04.545
Jangan mencoba menjadi terlalu pintar.

